title: Ep 108: Backwards Law & Not Giving a F#ck
description: In this episode I cover the book "The Subtle Art of Not Giving a Fuck" by Mark Manson and the paradoxical Backwards Law. How is it that the less we give a shit, the better we do at something? I explore all this and more, so get your life and get super deep on it, bros.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
